SuperTonic 3 — attribution notice

This directory contains a native MLX (Swift) reimplementation of the
SuperTonic 3 text-to-speech model by Supertone Inc.

Model: https://huggingface.co/Supertone/supertonic-3
Reference implementation: https://github.com/supertone-inc/supertonic

The model weights consumed by this implementation were format-converted from
the original ONNX exports (fp32, opset 19) in the `onnx/` directory of
`Supertone/supertonic-3` to MLX safetensors. These are MODIFIED FILES in the
sense of the license: the numerical values are unchanged, but the container
format, tensor key names, and Conv weight axis order ([O,I,K] -> [O,K,I])
differ from the originals. The classifier-free-guidance scale and Euler
integration step that are baked into the original vector_estimator.onnx graph
are factored out into runtime code here.

